           SHORT="KUPS is a powerful and easy-to-use CUPS front-end for KDE."
cat << EOF

KUPS provides a powerful management tool for CUPS. It allows users to manage 
printers and classes (enable/disable, add to/remove from class, configure 
driver, ...), to add them via an easy-to-use "add printer wizard", and to 
configure the CUPS daemon through a graphical configuration tool. 

EOF
